 />\n係就係好轉左 但係隔幾個月又有 又要搽<br />\n我幾個月前又生 仆街我以為好返 <br />\ne幾日又生 屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"類固醇搽過唔好就唔好再搽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會越搽越嚴重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T21:24:36.000Z","msg":"但有時初發唔搽佢又愈發愈大攤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac9bb99ce8a435a7fc9d62d6847d9d85f49e8c3","tid":976280,"uid":26274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T21:48:13.000Z","msg":"希望快點有得醫"},{"pid":"334e84c0b6bf3a0bb096d3b6e6f6de139c5e4a5b","tid":976280,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T22:05:49.000Z","msg":"讀書時無同學有，依家出街十個有一個有濕疹"},{"pid":"d257cb1e50b483387d1fb6b690f45cbefde2849d","tid":976280,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T22:32:17.000Z","msg":"以前啲人窮，明明唔食得海鮮都無機會食<br />\n所以無濕疹<br />\n依家個海污染勁好多<br />\n唔受得海鮮馬上現形<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361037228c287e15853c3c658209936c7b919a63","tid":976280,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d257cb1e50b483387d1fb6b690f45cbefde2849d","tid":976280,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T22:32:17.000Z","msg":"以前啲人窮，明明唔食得海鮮都無機會食<br />\n所以無濕疹<br />\n依家個海污染勁好多<br />\n唔受得海鮮馬上現形<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T00:00:24.000Z","msg":"原來因為爭鮮"},{"pid":"15403fb863991204e00fad66fa21fa9cfe110e31","tid":976280,"uid":43518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T22:56:31.000Z","msg":"30年黎都無濕疹 上年無啦啦有<br />\n仲要只係隻眼有濕疹 唔可以亂咁搽野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a0539f84c3f79dfd7824f173faa5b2ad39afbd","tid":976280,"uid":87635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"我都係近3，4年先有，響頸同肚位<br />\n想知可以點好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389cd40c8108f593fde7e2f351b9d12b93a7982d","tid":976280,"uid":18082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"空氣問題<br />\n<br />\n次次去旅行濕疹就好番晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d0d7e183e43c3847cea89961e5b3817ef9939f","tid":976280,"uid":22560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"389cd40c8108f593fde7e2f351b9d12b93a7982d","tid":976280,"uid":18082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"空氣問題<br />\n<br />\n次次去旅行濕疹就好番晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T02:20:40.000Z","msg":"我都係!!!!<br />\n一去旅行自動好返，一返香港又發<br />\n食藥都無咁準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff435fe4640006d542049a04ca79363bec8bbbd9","tid":976280,"uid":196552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"我生左濕疹30年<br />\n到後期真係紅晒出晒水痕都瞓唔著咁<br />\n之後戒晒口西醫試左三年唔掂轉睇中醫<br />\n都只係keep到唔會去到瞓唔著咁<br />\n但係我而家離開左香港一年<br />\n呢一年係完全冇睇過任何中西醫皮膚科之類<br />\n亦都冇用任何cream呀止痕既野<br />\n黎到第二個月己經停左出水晚晚瞓得好好<br />\n到半年果陣我見好左咁多<br />\n試下食返牛同海鮮<br />\n係完全唔會有事<br />\n到而家一年過去<br />\n我個程度係直頭濕疹印開始退<br />\n<br />\n咁你話我點解會生濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f0f753f58faa00ed1ad334cface51a7b54b661","tid":976280,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"我都係受害者之一<br />\n早幾年一發就勁嚴重<br />\nd濕疹會出好似水又白白嘅野真係街都唔敢出<br />\n好彩睇到個好醫生都叫做好得番<br />\n但係每年都仲會出少少<br />\n所以我都唔太敢一次食好多海鮮<br />\n暫時都叫控制得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb10a3c86f9b10a006e3f11bbc3bd3aeadace9c2","tid":976280,"uid":212487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"醫生話其實個個都有濕疹底<br />\n係睇幾時發同咩程度<br />\n有人細細個就有 有D 三十幾四十歲先爆<br />\n利申：有濕疹十幾年"},{"pid":"dcff8b7f10ce245716a2c30757869b9c75e69b78","tid":976280,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:59:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人係鼻樑位有濕疹？即係戴眼鏡兩粒膠嗰個位<br />\n<br />\n近視接近300度，但係嗰個位有濕疹戴親眼鏡就會因為壓住更加痕，試過由膠托轉去鈦金屬托都係一樣，副眼鏡就算幾輕都冇改善到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家考慮緊做激光，戴唔到眼鏡睇嘢好麻煩"},{"pid":"8ffbc61d4c1fbd244b2eeb4960495bdeccc96b03","tid":976280,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f0f753f58faa00ed1ad334cface51a7b54b661","tid":976280,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"我都係受害者之一<br />\n早幾年一發就勁嚴重<br />\nd濕疹會出好似水又白白嘅野真係街都唔敢出<br />\n好彩睇到個好醫生都叫做好得番<br />\n但係每年都仲會出少少<br />\n所以我都唔太敢一次食好多海鮮<br />\n暫時都叫控制得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T19:00:39.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意介紹嗰位醫生係邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}